'''狗哨'''是一种特殊的[[哨子_(器物)|哨子]]，大部分人類無法聽見狗哨发出的声音，但[[狗|狗]]和[[貓|貓]]能聽見狗哨發出的聲音。它是由[[法蘭西斯·高爾頓|法蘭西斯·高爾頓]]于1876年发明的<ref name="Galton1883">Galton, Francis (1883). [http://www.galton.org/books/human-faculty/index.html ''Inquiries into Human Faculty and its Development''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.galton.org/books/human-faculty/index.html |date=20210411035222 }}, p. 26-27</ref>，當時他發明狗哨是為了测试哪些[[频率|频率]]范围的聲音可以被動物聽見。

儿童能聽見的聲音頻率最高為20[[赫兹|千赫兹]]，中年人只能聽到最高為15–17[[赫兹|千赫兹]]的聲音。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Frequency Range of Human Hearing|url=http://hypertextbook.com/facts/2003/ChrisDAmbrose.shtml|work=The Physics Factbook|access-date=2020-10-23|archive-date=2020-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200520220413/https://hypertextbook.com/facts/2003/ChrisDAmbrose.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>狗可以聽見大约为45[[赫兹|千赫兹]]的聲音，而猫更是能聽見64[[赫兹|千赫兹]]的聲音。<ref name="Krantz">{{Cite book|last=Krantz|first=Les|title=Power of the Dog: Things Your Dog Can Do That You Can't|publisher=MacMillan|date=2009|pages=35–37|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=0l6jeMrA184C&pg=PA36|isbn=978-0312567224}}</ref> <ref name="Strain">{{Cite web|title=How Well Do Dogs and Other Animals Hear?|url=http://www.lsu.edu/deafness/HearingRange.html|accessdate=July 21, 2012|author=Strain|date=2010|first=George M.|work=Prof. Strain's website|publisher=School of Veterinary Medicine, Louisiana State University|archive-date=2008-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080817141938/http://www.lsu.edu/deafness/HearingRange.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>大多数狗哨發出的聲音频率在23至54[[赫兹|千赫兹]]之間<ref>{{Citation|title=Why Do Dogs Like Balls?: More Than 200 Canine Quirks, Curiosities, and Conundrums Revealed|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=uqe_I8Q83yAC&pg=PA116|year=2008|journal=Sterling Publishing Company, Inc|pages=116|last=Caroline Coile|first=D.|last2=Bonham|first2=Margaret H.|access-date=2011-08-07|isbn=9781402750397}}</ref>，這段頻率的聲音人類無法聽見。

狗哨的优点在於不会像普通哨子那样產生刺耳的声音，因此狗哨可以用于训练或指挥动物且避免影響到周圍的人。

